OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,FTwo Stormont ministers have pledged to
OL,7,Fwork together in progressing a baby
OL,8,Floss certificate scheme in Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FFinance Minister Caoimhe Archibald
OL,12,Fsaid she would be liaising with Health
OL,13,FMinister Robin Swann over the
OL,14,Fcertificates for parents who have lost
OL,15,Fa baby during pregnancy before 24
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,18,FUnder current legislation, the death
OL,19,Fof a baby is only officially
OL,20,Frecognised if it occurs after the 24th
OL,21,Fweek of pregnancy.
