OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,FThe UK Government launched a baby loss
OL,7,Fcertificate scheme earlier this year
OL,8,Fdesigned to recognise the grief of
OL,9,Fparents who lose a baby early in a
OL,10,Fpregnancy has been launched.
OL,12,FThe voluntary scheme offers those who
OL,13,Fexperience a loss pre-24 weeks'
OL,14,Fgestation a certificate to formally
OL,15,Frecognise the devastating impact.
OL,17,FThe Stormont Assembly discussed a
OL,18,Fprivate members' motion on the issue
OL,19,Fon Monday evening.
