OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,FMs Archibald said: "I want to pay
OL,7,Ftribute to those women and parents,
OL,8,Fwho have gone through the heartache of
OL,9,Flosing a baby during pregnancy, for
OL,10,Fshining a light on this issue and for
OL,11,Fsharing their own stories publicly to
OL,12,Fencourage change.
OL,14,F"Officials in the General Registration
OL,15,FOffice, within my department, will be
OL,16,Fworking with working with colleagues
OL,17,Fin the Department of Health to
OL,18,Fconsider how a baby loss certificate
OL,19,Fscheme could be implemented here.
