OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,F"While a certificate will not reverse
OL,7,For undo the pain which such a loss
OL,8,Finflicts on women and families, the
OL,9,Fintroduction of a voluntary
OL,10,Fcertificate scheme may in some way
OL,11,Fhelp parents to process their loss.
OL,13,F"I am committed to working together
OL,14,Fwith the Health Minister to take this
OL,15,Fscheme forward."
OL,17,FMr Swann said "Losing a baby is an
OL,18,Fimmensely painful experience for any
OL,19,Ffamily to have to endure.
