OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,F"I am also acutely aware that losing a
OL,7,Fbaby in the early stages of pregnancy
OL,8,Fwithout the opportunity to officially
OL,9,Fdocument the loss can further compound
OL,10,Fthe grief for some parents.
OL,12,F"Parents and families who very sadly
OL,13,Ffind themselves in this position can
OL,14,Fbe assured that my department is
OL,15,Fcontinuing to engage with counterparts
OL,16,Fin the Department of Health and Social
OL,17,FCare in England on this important
OL,18,Fmatter.
