OL,3,CStormont ministers to work together on
OL,4,Cbaby lost certificate scheme
OL,6,F"The scheme has just recently been
OL,7,Fintroduced there so we are still in
OL,8,Fthe early stages of this process but
OL,9,Fwe are committed to finding a viable
OL,10,Fsolution that will work for Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,F"I am grateful to have the Finance
OL,14,FMinister's backing and my officials
OL,15,Fwill work with the Department of
OL,16,FFinance on the next steps."
